maintext:
AUSTIN, Texas (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday afternoon’s drawing of the Texas Lottery’s “Daily 4 Day” game were:
7-1-1-4, FIREBALL: 1
(seven, one, one, four; FIREBALL: one)
